name: Die Heilige Sinfonie
effect: Increases all party members' Physical DMG by 55% for 300s.
description: Fischl's specialty. The exquisite presentation doth seem to communicate some incomprehensible enigma. When partaking, if one were to gaze upon Fischl, one might see her expectant gaze peek through the gaps of her fingers, which she is using to cover half her face... Is this also part of the mystery?
source: Fischl's specialty dish from cooking Cold Cut Platter.
